title: I'm in love with someone who's in love with someone
lyrics: tone I'm in love with someone Who's in love with someone And that someone will never be me So let me tell you about How i love the way you smile And that smile someday will be mine I don't know how to describe my feelings Blonde hair, brown eyes the way you see me Hoodie, beanie, baggy jeans and cap You just walked into the coffee shop While i instantly just watching you Wondering if i can know your name? That was my thought when we first met It's so weird but it's also sweet Cause i seem to fall in love with you I'm in love with someone Who's in love with someone And that someone someday will be me
